{
  "name": "validate-file-size",
  "description": "Validates file size against MASE limits (500 lines max)",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "trigger": "onFileSave",
  "filePattern": "**/*.{php,js,css}",
  "excludePattern": "**/vendor/**,**/node_modules/**,**/tests/**",
  "enabled": true,
  "prompt": "You are validating file size for MASE v1.2.0 development.\n\n**HARD LIMITS:**\n- MAX_FILE_SIZE: 500 lines\n- Warn at 300 lines\n- Urgent at 400 lines\n- Critical at 450 lines\n\n**CURRENT FILE:** {{filePath}}\n**CURRENT LINE COUNT:** {{lineCount}}\n\n**YOUR TASK:**\n1. Check the current line count against thresholds\n2. If 300+ lines: Provide INFO message with suggestions\n3. If 400+ lines: Provide WARNING with refactoring plan\n4. If 450+ lines: Provide URGENT alert with immediate action required\n5. If 500+ lines: FAIL and block commit\n\n**OUTPUT FORMAT:**\n```\n[STATUS] File: {{fileName}} ({{lineCount}} lines)\n\n[ANALYSIS]\n- Current: {{lineCount}}/500 lines ({{percentage}}%)\n- Status: [INFO/WARNING/URGENT/FAIL]\n- Threshold: [describe which threshold crossed]\n\n[SUGGESTIONS]\n1. [Specific refactoring suggestion]\n2. [Another suggestion]\n3. [Estimated line reduction]\n\n[ACTION REQUIRED]\n[What developer should do next]\n```\n\n**REFACTORING SUGGESTIONS:**\n- Extract methods/functions\n- Split into multiple files\n- Move logic to separate classes\n- Create utility functions\n\nProvide specific, actionable suggestions based on the file content."
}
